---
import Phones from '../assets/phones.png';
---

<section class="section-shell py-24 md:py-28">
  

  <div class="max-w-330 mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_minmax(0,1.12fr)] gap-8 md:gap-10 items-center">
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-155">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/8 px-4 py-2 text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-200">
        <span class="inline-block h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-trueview-blue to-trueview-red"></span>
        #1 trusted source for lab-tested supplements
      </span>

      <h2 class="mt-7 text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight">
        Supplements don’t regulate
        <br />
        themselves, <span class="text-trueview-red">so we do!</span>
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-8 text-gray-400 text-xl leading-relaxed">
        Reading lab reports shouldn’t turn into a full-time job.
        We translate complex data into Pass/Fails-covering
        accuracy, heavy metals, and microbes - just verify
        into your fingertips.
      </p>

      <a href="/waitlist" class="mt-10 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-[#2f6bff] to-[#1f49e8] px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/30 transition hover:brightness-110">
        Join the waitlist
        <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="relative min-h-125 md:min-h-180">
      <img
        src={Phones.src}
        width={Phones.width}
        height={Phones.height}
        alt="Vista previa de la app trueview en varios teléfonos"
        class="pointer-events-none select-none absolute -right-28 -top-44 w-180 max-w-none md:-right-20 md:-top-56 md:w-200"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
